<h2 id="watched-">Watched ğŸ“½</h2>
<ul>
<li>The Ugly Stepsister (2025)
<ul>
<li>A Norwegian &lsquo;The Substance&rsquo;. Similar themes of unattainable beauty standards with some gruesome body horror. It&rsquo;s a dark fairy tale/horror take on the Cinderella story. It&rsquo;s good, not for the squeamish. One you may need to recover from.</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>The Flash (2023)
<ul>
<li>Mostly annoying multiverse stuff but was surprised to hear Michael Keaton&rsquo;s Batman is in it, so I had to check out those bits.</li>
